data.description: Gorgeous 4 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom 2559 SQFT in Legend Point. Situated on an oversized corner lot with great privacy! This home is loaded with upgrades that add to the industrial/mid century design of the home. The wood burning fire place is encased in a gorgeous sheet metal is the focal point of heel living room. The light fixtures throughout have been upgraded and the appliances in the kitchen are fit for a gourmet kitchen. There is a bottlers pantry or bar area between the kitchen and formal dining area that is perfect for entertaining. Right off the entrance is an enclosed office with glass panel doors. Added cabinetry in the laundry room are great for additional storage. The upstairs family room is spacious with plenty of room to hang out on movie nights or game nights. The owners suite is spacious with a stunning industrial style ceiling fan, framed mirrors in the spacious on suite, separate soaking tub and walk in shower. This back yard is stunning. The patio was extended with pavers and crushed granite stones. Porch swings have been added the covered back patio and are perfect for taking in evenings and enjoying the oversized lot. A shed has also been added to the backyard and it has electrical and AC. Half has been converted into a remote office and half is used for storage. A new elementary school and sports complex are both under construction within 3 minutes of the home and will be huge assets to this community. Schedule a showing today for this unique gem of a home!
